<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.2">
<l>kañcaṉ viṭṭa veñci ṉatta kaḷiṟa ṭartta kāḷai yeṉṟum</l>
<l>vañca mēvi vanta pēyi ṉuyirai yuṇṭa māya ṉeṉṟum</l>
<l>ceñco lāḷar nīṭu nāṅkait tēva tēva ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>pañci yaṉṉa mella ṭiyāḷ pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “Youth who destroyed the fiery, raging elephant that Kaṁsa sent,”</l>
<l>Saying, “Māyaṉ who consumed the life of the demoness</l>
<l rend="indent">who came being covered in a disguise,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “God of gods in spacious Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with those of perfect words,”</l>
<l>The one with soft feet like cotton sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
